description:
EcBus: Table containing metadata describing a single Ericsson eCPRI bus connection in a 5G NR network.

dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
Area_Name: Name of the network area (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
CellId: Identifier of the cell related to the eCPRI bus.
Id2: Redundant identifier, mirroring CellId.
Id3:  A seemingly arbitrary identifier.
vsDataType: Type of data, specifying it's eCPRI bus data.
vsDataFormatVersion:  Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
EcBus.ecBusConnectorRef: Reference string identifying the eCPRI bus connector.
EcBus.ecBusId:  Identifier of the eCPRI bus.
EcBus.equipmentSupportFunctionRef: Reference string identifying the supporting equipment function.
EcBus.ecBusConnectionType: Type of eCPRI bus connection (e.g., EC).
